---
layout: base.njk
title: 网站地图
description: DeepSeek 对话指南站的主要页面、核心教程与文章索引。
permalink: /sitemap/index.html
---

<div style="max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto;">
  <h1 style="font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 12px;">网站地图</h1>
  <p style="color: #64748b; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 32px;">本站面向 DeepSeek 网页对话场景，以下为可公开访问的主要页面与教程入口（不含后台管理路径）。</p>

  <section style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
    <h2 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;">主要页面</h2>
    <ul style="line-height: 2; padding-left: 20px; color: #334155;">
      {% for loc in locales %}
      <li><a href="{{ loc.path }}">{{ loc.label }}首页</a></li>
      {% endfor %}
      <li><a href="/posts/">技术文章列表</a></li>
      <li><a href="/privacy/">隐私政策</a></li>
      <li><a href="/feed.xml">RSS 订阅</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
    <h2 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;">核心教程（多语言）</h2>
    <ul style="line-height: 2; padding-left: 20px; color: #334155;">
      {% for post in collections.pillarPosts %}
      {% if (post.data.locale or 'zh-CN') == 'zh-CN' %}
      <li><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></li>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
    <h2 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;">简体中文教程与文章</h2>
    <ul style="line-height: 2; padding-left: 20px; color: #334155;">
      {% for post in collections.indexablePosts %}
      {% if not post.data.translationKey %}
      <li><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a> <span style="color:#94a3b8;font-size:13px;">{{ post.date | dateFilter }}</span></li>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </section>

  <p style="margin-top: 32px;"><a href="/">&larr; 返回首页</a></p>
</div>
